@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Services";
}

<div class="container-fluid pb-4">
    <p class="text-center mb-2 pt-4 pb-4">SERVICES</p>
    <div class="accordion" id="cleaningAccordion">
        <div class="accordion-item">
            <h2 class="accordion-header" id="headingOne">
            <button class="accordion-button" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseOne" aria-expanded="true" aria-controls="collapseOne">
                Deep Cleaning
            </button>
            </h2>
            <div id="collapseOne" class="accordion-collapse collapse show" aria-labelledby="headingOne" data-bs-parent="#cleaningAccordion">
                <div class="accordion-body">
                    Deep cleanings range from $150-200. This thorough cleaning service is designed to reach the 
                    deep grime and dirt in your home. It covers areas that aren't traditionally covered by a regular
                    cleaning service. The price may vary based on the size and condition of your home.<br><br>
                    <button class="custom-nav-button p-1"><a asp-controller="Home" asp-action="AppointmentForm">Schedule</a></button>                
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="accordion-item">
            <h2 class="accordion-header" id="headingTwo">
            <button class="accordion-button" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseTwo" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseTwo">
                Standard Cleaning
            </button>
            </h2>
            <div id="collapseTwo" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="headingTwo" data-bs-parent="#cleaningAccordion">
                <div class="accordion-body">
                    Standard cleanings are typically charged at $70. This service is ideal for maintaining the cleanliness
                    of your home, this service includes tasks like dusting, vacuuming, sweeping, and mopping floors.<br><br>
                    <button class="custom-nav-button p-1"><a asp-controller="Home" asp-action="AppointmentForm">Schedule</a></button>                
                    </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="accordion-item">
            <h2 class="accordion-header" id="headingThree">
            <button class="accordion-button" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseThree" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseThree">
                Furniture Cleaning
            </button>
            </h2>
            <div id="collapseThree" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="headingThree" data-bs-parent="#cleaningAccordion">
                <div class="accordion-body">
                    Furniture cleanings are typically charged at $25 per item. This service focuses on cleaning your
                    furniture to help remove dust, dirt, and stains. We will ensure that your sofas, chairs, and other
                    pieces of furniture are fresh and clean.<br><br>
                    <button class="custom-nav-button p-1"><a asp-controller="Home" asp-action="AppointmentForm">Schedule</a></button>                
                    </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="accordion-item">
            <h2 class="accordion-header" id="headingFour">
            <button class="accordion-button" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseFour" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseFour">
                Move-In/Out Cleaning
            </button>
            </h2>
            <div id="collapseFour" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="headingFour" data-bs-parent="#cleaningAccordion">
                <div class="accordion-body">
                    Move-In/Out cleanings are typically charged at $100. This service is tailored for homes
                    either before you move in or after you move out. We ensure that every nook and cranny gets
                    attention, providing a clean slate for the next occupant.<br><br>
                    <button class="custom-nav-button p-1"><a asp-controller="Home" asp-action="AppointmentForm">Schedule</a></button>                
                    </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="accordion-item">
            <h2 class="accordion-header" id="headingFive">
            <button class="accordion-button" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseFive" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseFive">
                Carpet Cleaning
            </button>
            </h2>
            <div id="collapseFive" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="headingFive" data-bs-parent="#cleaningAccordion">
                <div class="accordion-body">
                    Carpet cleanings are typically charged at $25 per room. This equipment is performed with specialized equipment
                    for cleaning carpets. We will ensure that your carpets are cleaned thoroughly, removing dirt, allergens, 
                    and stains. This is a cost-effective solution for maintaining your carpets.<br><br>
                    <button class="custom-nav-button p-1"><a asp-controller="Home" asp-action="AppointmentForm">Schedule</a></button>                
                    </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>